"Open fire against this Saberback ans his dinosaurs!!!!" yelled 
Hydras"Cyclonus, set the defences and open fire against Saberback".

-----Mensaje original----- 
From: Super Cyclonus
Sent: Monday, July 25, 2011 6:55 AM
To: nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com
Subject: Re: Hydras and Predacons

> <OLD>
>
> "Why are you attacking us Saberback?"replied Hyrdas in his most diplomatic
> tone "So far I remember, I or my preds never have disturbed you"
>
> Hydras liked to avoid a conflict he had more importand issues to atend

SABERBACK just continued to float in the air above the dinosaurs as
they rushed towards HYDRAS' base. They were a few miles away now, and
the lead dinosaurs, as HYDRAS could see them, were looking ragged, as
if they were being forced to run beyond their limits to run.

A dark twisted smile appears on SABERBACK's face, "Ahh yes, Predacons
and their foolish little squabbles. You shall fall beneath the wave my
master will bring." The dinsaurs continue running forward.

Meanwhile HYDRAS recieved a message from FRACTYL who was still back at
the base helping to monitor things, "Sir. I am detecting some sort of
harmonic pulse coming from who ever that is you are facing. Perhaps
that is how he is controlling the dinosaurs?"
